{"lastModified":1771253212479,"uri":"c::17951852342::vessel::322a8fe0-37af-11f0-a4e2-f77743b06a1e","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nIntroducing Kyveli, a charming 4-cabin sailing yacht, the Bavaria Cruiser 46, crafted in 2015 and now based in Marina Alimos, Greece.\n\nKyveli warmly accommodates up to 8 guests in its four inviting double cabins, where pillows and blankets are thoughtfully provided for a cozy stay.\n\nFeaturing three toilets with a shower, Kyveli ensures convenience and comfort throughout your sailing adventure.Equipped with a rolling mainsail, solar panels, salon GPS plotter, bimini, and bow thruster, Kyveli promises a smooth and enjoyable journey on the water. Entertain yourself with the audio system, inside and outside speakers.\n\nIn the fully-equipped galley, you’ll find everything you need to prepare delightful meals, including an oven, cooker, sink, and kitchen utensils, allowing you to indulge in culinary delights while onboard.\n\nEmbark on an unforgettable sailing experience aboard Kyveli, where comfort, convenience, and relaxation await amidst the stunning beauty of the Greek coastline.","blueprint":{"name":"KYVELI","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::322a8fe0-37af-11f0-a4e2-f77743b06a1e::assets::aaf37140-37b3-11f0-be10-996975cddc98/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::322a8fe0-37af-11f0-a4e2-f77743b06a1e::assets::aaf1c390-37b3-11f0-8e32-7b09e718a00e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::322a8fe0-37af-11f0-a4e2-f77743b06a1e::assets::aafbfcc0-37b3-11f0-beeb-4f341f7c1cb3/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::322a8fe0-37af-11f0-a4e2-f77743b06a1e::assets::aafa2800-37b3-11f0-bc3d-533a016677f2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::322a8fe0-37af-11f0-a4e2-f77743b06a1e::assets::aaf6f3b0-37b3-11f0-bc3d-533a016677f2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::322a8fe0-37af-11f0-a4e2-f77743b06a1e::assets::aaf93da0-37b3-11f0-bc3d-533a016677f2/{imageVariant}","/medi